listings.comment: Nawsher and crew did a great job. I don't have much knowledge when it comes to getting domains and setting up websites but they patiently worked with me until we got everything squared away. they then got me a beautiful starting website! they were very accommodating when I had to make adjustments with things like numbers of pages. Very grateful and happy with the final product!

listings.title: build wordpress website development, business website or wordpress blog website
listings.comment: Nawsher Ali was instrumental in designing a website for my teaching and traveling business, showcasing commendable politeness, cooperation, and language fluency throughout the process. However, there were notable hiccups concerning attention to detail and professionalism, leading to multiple revisions where functionality issues like broken links and improper formatting were prevalent. Despite these setbacks, his quick responsiveness and willingness to take feedback ensured the website is now in a better condition, though there's room for improvement in meeting expectations promptly in future projects.

listings.title: build wordpress website development, business website or wordpress blog website
listings.comment: Nawsher was great to work with. This project took longer than expected due to interruptions on his end, and my end but he continued to see the project through to completion. I'm please with my new business website, and would work with Nawsher again.
